"Drupal core does not immediately delete temporary file. For webform "
"submissions it is recommended that temporary files are immediately "
"deleted."
msgstr ""
"El nucli de Drupal no elimina immediatament el fitxer temporal. Per a "
"enviaments de formularis web, es recomana que els fitxers temporals "
"s'eliminin immediatament."

