"de contingut (mime) de l'adjunt."

msgid ""
"Make sure the attachment URL/Path is publicly accessible. The "
"attachment's URL/path will never be displayed to end users."
msgstr ""
"Assegura't que l'URL/camí de l'adjunt sigui accessible públicament. "
"L'URL/camí de l'adjunt mai no es mostrarà als usuaris finals."

msgid ""
"Webforms must first be <a href=\":href\">created</a> before "
"referencing them."
msgstr ""
"Els formularis web s'han de <a href=\":href\">crear</a> abans de "
"referenciar-los."

